===== To build =====

Download cmake:
http://www.cmake.org/cmake/resources/software.html

Create a build directory outside of the source directory (e.g., ../_buildmcg)
and cd to it (cd ../_buildmcg)

Run cmake and configure it once to see the options, change them as desired:
cmake-gui ../mcgeometry

Compile using make (or XCode or Eclipse or whatever other build system you
chose with cmake)

===== TARGETS =====
make lib:
    create the mcgeometry and transupport libraries

make check:
    build unit tests and runs them with CTest

make examples:
    build the examples

make doc:
	build doxygen documentation (experimental)

make install:
    install headers and libraries to the prefix directory
